<BaseLayout title="Voidless Tale">
  <h2>The Game</h2>
  <p>Voidless Tale blends vibrant pixel art with souls-like combat. Explore mirrored domains of Heaven and Hell as you hunt for memory scraps tied to the seven deadly sins.</p>
  <section>
    <h3>Core Systems</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>2D side-scrolling movement with melee combos and absorbable skills.</li>
      <li>Paper-doll gear that supports palette swaps and modular equipment.</li>
      <li>Veinshard skill system: capture enemy abilities and slot them into your action bar.</li>
      <li>Craft keys to confront celestial and infernal bosses.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
